Interface DatabaseAPI.StatementCommon

All Superinterfaces:
AutoCloseable
All Known Subinterfaces:
DatabaseAPI.Query, DatabaseAPI.Update
Enclosing interface:
DatabaseAPI
public static interface DatabaseAPI.StatementCommon extends AutoCloseable
Common shared API between DatabaseAPI.Query and DatabaseAPI.Update. This supports prepared statements within the general mechanisms of this API.
Author:
Donal Fellows
